data.description: Welcome to your dream mountain chalet in the coveted private gated community of Lake Arrowhead! This beautiful split-level home is situated in a prime location, set back away from the noise and hustle of the city, yet conveniently close to all the amenities you could ever need. Mere minutes from the lake, Lake Arrowhead is Georgia's second largest private man-made lake with 11 miles of shoreline, that stretches over 540 acres.  As you step inside, you'll immediately feel at home. The spacious living area is perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family, featuring large windows that let in plenty of natural light and offer stunning views of the serene forest. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with high-end appliances, ample storage space, and a island perfect for meal prep.  The upper level boasts three bedrooms, each with its own unique charm and character. The master suite is a peaceful oasis, complete with spacious walk-in closets, a luxurious spa like en suite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. Downstairs, you'll find a versatile living space that can be used as an additional bedroom, a home office, or a game room. There's even an option to add a second bedroom downstairs, making this the perfect multi-generational or income-producing property.  The community itself is a haven of relaxation and recreation, with tons of amenities to enjoy. Whether you're looking for a game of pickleball, a round of tennis, a day on the lake, or a dip in the pool, you'll find it all right here. If you're a golf enthusiast, you'll love being just steps away from the greens.  With its idyllic location, stunning views, and luxurious features, this mountain chalet is truly a must-see. Don't miss your chance to make it yours today!
